node.text: When Hobbs Kessler passes you, the race is as good as done. With his speed and stamina, @Hobbs_Kessler posted official times like 3:34.36 in the 1500m (No. 1 U.S. & All-Time Rank), 8:39.04 in the 2-mile (No. 1 U.S. Rank), and 1:49.67 in the 800m (No. 3 U.S. Rank). May be an image of text that says '2020 ONGR 2021 HOBBS KESSLER GATORADE PLAYER OF THE YEAR Hobbs Kessler left opponents in the dust as he blazed around the track. His speed and stamina allowed him to earn two Michigan state titles and break numerous records. Ranked No. in the 2-mile and 1500m races, the future pro-runner is not to be taken lightly on the track. BOYS TRACK FIELD'.
